# Prerequisites
track = d.create_track().add_saw_wave(max_vel=5.0, duration=15.0, periods=3)

def apply_settings(mode: int, p_in: float, i_in: float, d_in: float, bias: float, initial_i: float = 0, plot_exclude_wheels: list = [2]):
    d.set_global_velocity(0)
    d.set_global_adaptive_state(initial_i)
    d.set_global_control_params(p_in, i_in, d_in, bias, mode)
    result = track.run()
    d.set_global_velocity(0)
    d.set_global_adaptive_state(0)
    result.plot(plot_exclude_wheels)
    result.plot_setpoint_v_velocity(plot_exclude_wheels)
    result.plot_all(plot_exclude_wheels)
    return result
